reviewText: This is fast paced. It gives you a lot in a short period of time.  I prefer the Rick Steves presentation on the same subject over this one. He is a very interesting speaker and appears on his videos.  On this video, the narrator never appears.

Spends about 15 seconds on each site. Narration is adequate and accurate, but not exactly exciting. With more detail and background stories for each site, it would be more interesting and more helpful.
